@startuml fig2_meta_harness_lifecycle_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName "Noto Sans CJK SC, DejaVu Sans"
skinparam padding 4
skinparam wrapWidth 110

title 图2  Meta-Harness 组件生命周期时序流程图\n——从发现到激活的完整控制流，含四级安全链路与热加载回滚

actor "用户 / 系统" as User
participant "HarnessRuntime\n核心调度" as Runtime <<L1>>
participant "ComponentDiscovery\n发现器" as Discovery <<L1>>
participant "ComponentLoader\n加载器" as Loader <<L1>>
participant "ComponentRegistry\n注册表" as Registry <<L2>>
participant "CompatibilityValidator\n兼容性校验" as Validator <<L3>>
participant "Optimizer\n元层优化器" as Optimizer <<Meta>>
participant "SandboxValidator\n沙箱验证" as Sandbox <<L5>>
participant "ABShadowTester\n影子测试" as ABTest <<L5>>
participant "PolicyVeto\n宪法否决" as Policy <<L5>>
participant "AutoRollback\n回滚观察" as Rollback <<L5>>
participant "GraphVersionMgr\n版本管理" as VersionMgr <<L3>>
participant "Component\n(实例)" as Component <<L4>>

autonumber

== Phase 0: 启动准备 ==

User -> Runtime : 启动 Meta-Harness
activate Runtime

Runtime -> Registry : 创建注册表
Runtime -> Discovery : 配置发现器
Runtime -> Loader : 配置加载器

Runtime -> Runtime : boot()

== Phase 1: 发现 (Discovery) ==

Runtime -> Discovery : discover_all()
activate Discovery

Discovery -> Discovery : scan_bundled()\nmetaharness/components/*
Discovery -> Discovery : scan_templates()\n模板库中的组件骨架
Discovery -> Discovery : scan_market()\n组件市场（远程）
Discovery -> Discovery : scan_custom()\n用户自定义路径

Discovery -> Discovery : 冲突解决\n(高优先级覆盖低优先级)

Discovery --> Runtime : 返回候选列表\nList[ComponentCandidate]
deactivate Discovery

== Phase 2: 静态验证 (Static Validation) ==

loop 每个候选组件
    Runtime -> Loader : validate_candidate()
    activate Loader

    Loader -> Loader : 检查 harness_version
    Loader -> Loader : 检查 bins / env 依赖
    Loader -> Loader : 解析 harness.component.json

    alt 验证失败
        Loader --> Runtime : 错误列表
        Runtime -> Runtime : 记录失败\nphase=FAILED
    else 验证通过
        Loader --> Runtime : 空错误列表\nphase=VALIDATED_STATIC
    end
    deactivate Loader
end

Runtime -> Runtime : 过滤已禁用组件\nconfig.enabled=False → 跳过

== Phase 3: 依赖解析 ==

Runtime -> Loader : resolve_load_order()
activate Loader

Loader -> Loader : Kahn 算法拓扑排序
Loader -> Loader : 检测循环依赖

alt 存在循环依赖
    Loader --> Runtime : CircularDependencyError
    Runtime -> Runtime : 标记循环插件为 FAILED
else 无循环
    Loader --> Runtime : 排序后的候选列表
end
deactivate Loader

== Phase 4: 注册与接口声明 (Register) ==

loop 按依赖顺序加载每个组件
    Runtime -> Loader : load_component_class()
    activate Loader
    Loader -> Loader : import_module()
    Loader --> Runtime : Component Class
    deactivate Loader

    Runtime -> Component : 无参构造
    activate Component

    == Phase 4a: 接口声明 (declare_interface) ==

    Runtime -> Component : declare_interface(api)
    activate Component

    note right of Component
        declare_interface() 约束:
        - 同步执行
        - 无 I/O 操作
        - 幂等性保证
    end note

    Component -> Registry : declare_input("command", type="Command")
    Component -> Registry : declare_output("action", type="Action")
    Component -> Registry : declare_event("on_config_reload")

    Component --> Runtime : return
    deactivate Component

    == Phase 4b: 注册行为 (register) ==

    Runtime -> Component : register(api)

    Component -> Registry : register_connection_handler(...)
    Component -> Registry : register_hook(event, handler, kind)
    Component -> Registry : register_migration_adapter(...)

    alt register() 抛出异常
        Component --> Runtime : Exception
        Runtime -> Registry : rollback_component()
        Runtime -> Runtime : phase=FAILED, 继续下一组件
    else 注册成功
        Component --> Runtime : return
        deactivate Component

        Runtime -> Registry : commit_component()
        activate Registry

        note right of Registry
            原子性提交:
            1. 冲突检测 (ID/端口)
            2. 写入 pending 区
            3. 生成 pending mutation 记录
        end note

        alt 冲突检测失败
            Registry --> Runtime : RegistrationConflictError
            Runtime -> Registry : rollback_component()
        else 提交成功
            Registry --> Runtime : OK
        end
        deactivate Registry
    end
end

== Phase 5: 候选图组装 ==

Runtime -> VersionMgr : assemble_candidate_graph()
activate VersionMgr

VersionMgr -> VersionMgr : 从 pending 区收集所有组件
VersionMgr -> Validator : 兼容性校验 (五条规则)
activate Validator

Validator -> Validator : 1. 类型匹配\nConnection.source.Output\n== Connection.target.Input
Validator -> Validator : 2. 事件声明\ntrigger 事件必须显式声明
Validator -> Validator : 3. 输入完整性\nrequired=true 的 Input\n必须被 Connection 满足
Validator -> Validator : 4. ID 唯一性
Validator -> Validator : 5. 无环约束 (可选)

alt 校验失败
    Validator --> VersionMgr : 错误列表
    VersionMgr --> Runtime : AssemblyError
    Runtime -> Optimizer : 反馈负向奖励信号
    note right of Optimizer
        Optimizer 收到校验失败
        作为搜索的惩罚信号
        调整下一轮候选生成
    end note
else 校验通过
    Validator --> VersionMgr : 通过
    VersionMgr -> VersionMgr : 创建 candidate_graph_version\n(不可变快照)
    VersionMgr --> Runtime : candidate_version_id
end
deactivate Validator
deactivate VersionMgr

Runtime -> Runtime : phase=ASSEMBLED

== Phase 6: 动态验证 — 四级安全链路 ==

Runtime -> Sandbox : validate(candidate_version)
activate Sandbox

note right of Sandbox
    根据风险等级选择沙箱层级:
    V8/WASM (<1ms) — 简单逻辑
    gVisor (~50ms) — Python 脚本
    Firecracker (~30ms) — 高危操作
end note

== 第一级：沙箱验证 ==

Sandbox -> Sandbox : 在隔离环境中执行\n回归测试 + 历史失败重放
Sandbox -> Sandbox : 资源限制:\ntimeout / memory / network

alt 沙箱验证失败
    Sandbox --> Runtime : 拒绝
    Runtime -> Optimizer : 负向奖励 -R_fail
    note right of Optimizer
        记录失败轨迹到 Memory
        供反事实诊断使用
    end note
else 沙箱验证通过
    Sandbox -> ABTest : 进入第二级
end

== 第二级：A/B 影子测试 ==

activate ABTest

ABTest -> ABTest : 复制生产流量到候选配置\n候选输出仅记录，不影响用户
ABTest -> ABTest : 统计显著性检验\n配对 t 检验 / Wilcoxon

alt 候选配置劣于基线
    ABTest --> Runtime : 终止上线
    Runtime -> Optimizer : 记录差异报告
else 候选配置显著优于或持平基线
    ABTest -> Policy : 进入第三级
end
deactivate ABTest

== 第三级：Policy 宪法否决 ==

activate Policy

Policy -> Policy : 审查安全不变量
note right of Policy
    不可变规则:
    C-01: 资源硬顶约束
    C-02: 影子验证一致性
    C-03: 关键路径不可篡改
    C-04: Token 预算熔断
    C-05: 隐私泄露阻断
    ---
    R-01: 数据溯源强制 (科研)
    R-02: 不可重现性警报 (科研)
    R-03: 同行评审模拟 (科研)
end note

alt 违反不可变规则
    Policy --> Runtime : 宪法否决
    Runtime -> Optimizer : 强惩罚信号 -R_veto
else 通过宪法审查
    Policy -> Rollback : 进入第四级
end
deactivate Policy

== 第四级：自动回滚准备 ==

activate Rollback

Rollback -> VersionMgr : 创建 Checkpoint\n(当前 active graph 快照)
Rollback -> Rollback : 启动观察窗口\nmax(20 tasks, 300s)

Rollback --> Runtime : 安全链路全部通过
deactivate Rollback
deactivate Sandbox

Runtime -> Runtime : phase=VALIDATED_DYNAMIC

== Phase 7: 激活与提交 (Activate & Commit) ==

loop 按依赖顺序激活每个组件
    Runtime -> Component : activate(api)
    activate Component

    note right of Component
        activate() 约束:
        - 异步执行
        - I/O 允许
        - 30 秒超时
    end note

    Component -> Component : 初始化外部连接
    Component -> Component : 加载模型 / 分配资源
    Component -> Component : 启动后台服务

    alt 激活成功
        Component --> Runtime : return
        deactivate Component
        Runtime -> Registry : phase=ACTIVATED
    else 激活失败 / 超时
        Component --> Runtime : Exception
        deactivate Component
        Runtime -> Registry : phase=FAILED
        Runtime -> Runtime : 记录失败，继续下一组件
    end
end

Runtime -> VersionMgr : commit_graph(candidate_version_id)
activate VersionMgr

VersionMgr -> VersionMgr : 原子性切换:\ncandidate → active graph version
VersionMgr -> VersionMgr : 递增 graph_version_number
VersionMgr -> VersionMgr : 旧版本标记为 rollback_target

VersionMgr --> Runtime : committed_version_id
deactivate VersionMgr

Runtime -> Runtime : phase=COMMITTED

== Phase 7b: 热加载 — Suspend-Transform-Resume ==

opt "Optimizer 发起热替换（非首次启动）"

    Runtime -> Component : suspend()
    activate Component
    Component -> Component : 停止接收新消息
    Component -> Component : drain(timeout=30s)\n等待当前操作完成
    Component --> Runtime : state_snapshot
    deactivate Component

    Runtime -> VersionMgr : create_checkpoint(state_snapshot)

    note right of Runtime
        Transform 阶段:
        τ: S_old × ΔP → S_new
        Optimizer 同步生成 Python 转换逻辑
    end note

    Runtime -> Component : resume(new_state)
    activate Component
    Component -> Component : 注入迁移后的状态
    Component -> Component : 恢复消息处理
    Component --> Runtime : return
    deactivate Component

end

== Phase 8: 观察与回滚 (Observe & Rollback) ==

Runtime -> Rollback : 开始观察窗口
activate Rollback

loop "观察窗口内持续监控"
    Rollback -> Rollback : 采集健康指标:\n错误率 / 延迟 P99 / 资源异常
    Rollback -> Rollback : Z-Score 异常检测:\nT_new > μ(T_old) + 3σ(T_old)
end

alt 性能退化 / 异常行为
    Rollback -> Runtime : 触发回滚
    Runtime -> VersionMgr : rollback_to(rollback_target_version)
    activate VersionMgr
    VersionMgr -> VersionMgr : 恢复上一 stable Checkpoint
    VersionMgr -> VersionMgr : 切换 active graph pointer
    VersionMgr --> Runtime : rollback_complete
    deactivate VersionMgr

    Runtime -> Optimizer : 回滚事件 + 失败轨迹

    opt "同一意图连续 3 次回滚"
        Runtime -> Runtime : 标记为 Dead End\n写入 Memory 禁止重复
    end

else 观察窗口通过
    Rollback -> Runtime : 确认稳定
    Runtime -> VersionMgr : 标记版本为 stable
end
deactivate Rollback

== Phase 9: 运行状态 ==

Runtime --> User : BootResult\n(loaded, failed 列表)
deactivate Runtime

User -> Runtime : 正常运行中...\n组件图处理任务请求

== Phase 10: 关闭 (Shutdown) ==

User -> Runtime : 关闭请求
activate Runtime

Runtime -> Runtime : stop_all_services()

loop 按逆序反激活组件
    Runtime -> Component : deactivate()
    activate Component
    Component -> Component : 保存持久化状态
    Component -> Component : 关闭连接 / 释放资源
    Component --> Runtime : return
    deactivate Component
    Runtime -> Registry : phase=SUSPENDED
end

Runtime -> VersionMgr : 归档当前 graph version

Runtime --> User : 关闭完成
deactivate Runtime

@enduml
